name: Davidos
description: A wise and powerful leader, known for his strategic mind and musical talents. Davidos is revered for his ability to unite people and inspire hope in the darkest of times.

name: Reuvenos
description: The firstborn of the Celestial brothers, Reuvenos is known for his strength and loyalty. Despite past mistakes, he strives to redeem himself and protect his family.

name: Johnyos
description: A charismatic and adventurous spirit, Johnyos is known for his quick wit and adaptability. He often serves as a mediator between different factions.

name: Zeevios
description: A fierce warrior with the heart of a poet, Zeevios is as skilled in battle as he is in philosophy. His wisdom is sought after by many.

name: Yairos
description: Known for his unwavering faith and ability to bring light to darkness, Yairos is a beacon of hope for his people in times of trouble.

name: Benjaminos
description: The youngest of the Celestial brothers, Benjaminos is known for his speed and agility. His youthful energy often brings a fresh perspective to challenges.

name: Mendyos
description: A master of celestial technology, Mendyos is the go-to problem solver for complex issues. His inventions have saved countless lives.

name: Haimos
description: Haimos is renowned for his life-giving abilities. His power to heal and nurture makes him an invaluable asset to his people.

name: Shaios
description: A gifted orator and diplomat, Shaios has prevented countless conflicts with his words alone. His charisma is matched only by his wisdom.

name: Shlomoos
description: Known as the wisest of all Celestials, Shlomoos' judgment is sought after in matters both great and small. His decisions shape the future of his people.

name: Shmulos
description: A master of celestial agriculture, Shmulos ensures the abundance of resources for his people. His connection to nature is unparalleled.

name: Eliezeros
description: A formidable warrior and loyal friend, Eliezeros is known for his unwavering dedication to protecting the weak and upholding justice.

name: Elkanaeres
description: A visionary leader with the ability to see glimpses of the future, Elkanaeres guides his people through turbulent times with wisdom and foresight.

name: Aharoneres
description: The high priest of the Celestials, Aharoneres serves as a bridge between the mortal and divine realms. His prayers have miraculous effects.

name: Natieres
description: A master of celestial arts, Natieres brings beauty and inspiration to his people through his creations. His works are said to hold magical properties.

name: Mordechaieres
description: A skilled strategist and guardian of knowledge, Mordechaieres oversees the vast libraries of celestial wisdom. His intellect is a formidable weapon.

name: Menachemeres
description: Known as the great comforter, Menachemeres has the unique ability to soothe troubled souls and restore hope to the hopeless.

name: Arieleres
description: A master of celestial elements, Arieleres can control the very forces of nature. His power is both revered and feared.

name: Mennyeres
description: The keeper of celestial time, Mennyeres ensures the smooth flow of temporal energies. His mastery over time itself is unparalleled.

name: Pinchaseres
description: A zealous defender of celestial law, Pinchaseres ensures that justice is served swiftly and fairly. His judgment is as sharp as his celestial spear.

name: Simchaeres
description: The embodiment of joy and celebration, Simchaeres has the power to lift spirits and inspire happiness even in the darkest of times.

name: Israeleres
description: A celestial champion who has overcome countless trials, Israeleres serves as an inspiration to all. His indomitable spirit is legendary.

name: Menachemeres
description: A master of celestial alchemy, Menachemeres can transmute energies and matter, creating wonders beyond imagination.

name: Mordechaieres
description: The celestial chronicler, Mordechaieres records the history and prophecies of his people. His words have the power to shape reality.

name: Mordechaimeres
description: A celestial diplomat with unparalleled charm, Mordechaimeres can sway the hearts of even the most stubborn adversaries. His words are his greatest weapon.
